<plot>The Under-the-Bed monster is real, and the duty of protecting each new generation of a particular family from him falls from aunt to niece. "The Gift" is a story about duty, responsibility, and sacrificing for people you love. It also reminds us that sometimes the monsters who live beside us are far worse than the ones that live under our beds.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?560346</url></doc>
